README
-----
This sample project provides a command line tool to do RPN Calculator operations.


System requirements
-------------------

1. JDK 1.8
2. Maven Build tool (3.X.X)


Compiling project
----------------
Change directory path to the "Airwallex-Calculator" folder location and run as;
# mvn clean install

Above will build the project.

Run program
------------
Change directory path to the "target" folder location and run as;

#java -jar com.airwallex.calculator-1.0-jar-with-dependencies.jar

you will be asked for inputs  like;

Please enter parameters and operations as single whitespace separated list 
 eg: 5 4 3 + (If you want to quit type 'exit')  

 $ >

and if you provide like;
3 4

you will see the output as;

Stack : 3 4 
 

TestCases
---------

Test scenarios are added as Junit tests.(src/test/java/com/airwallex/calculator/test/CalculatorTest.java)

